        "content": "<p>JonasKruckenberg edited <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13479\">PR #13479</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Currently <code>cranelift-codegen</code> fails to build for <code>riscv64gc-unknown-none-elf</code> because the <code>powi</code> builtins are not available when targeting <code>no_std</code>. This PR fixes that by pulling in libm. </p>\n<p>Replacing <code>powi</code> with essentially <code>powf</code> _might_ be slower, but I don't think this change is going to show up in benchmarks.</p>\n</blockquote>",
        "id": 597516247,
        "sender_full_name": "Wasmtime GitHub notifications bot",
        "timestamp": 1779708238
    },
    {
